OL,3,CEconomy grows less than previously
OL,4,Cthought, figures show
OL,6,FLiz McKeown, director of economic
OL,7,Fstatistics for the ONS, said the
OL,8,Fupdated GDP figures for 2023 and 2024
OL,9,Finclude new annual survey data, VAT
OL,10,Freturns and updated information about
OL,11,Fthe relative size of each industry for
OL,12,Fthe first time.
OL,14,F"However, after taking on these
OL,15,Fimprovements, the quarterly growth
OL,16,Fpath across the last 18 months is
OL,17,Fvirtually unchanged," she said.
