OL,6,FIt prompted Chancellor Rachel Reeves
OL,7,Fto say she was "under no illusion
OL,8,Fabout the scale of the challenge" the
OL,9,Fcountry faces, and that "change will
OL,10,Fnot happen overnight".
OL,12,F"Two quarters of positive economic
OL,13,Fgrowth does not make up for 14 years
OL,14,Fof stagnation," she added.
